=== Removing roads ===
There are two ways to remove road sections (besides the dynamite [[File:en/Manual/Clear title.png|Dynamite tool]] tool)

*The easy way to remove roads is to hold down the CTRL key.

#To '''remove a section''' of roads, '''hold CTRL''' and '''click & drag''' along existing road section. Just as you would when building roads.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/AutoroadTut7.png|none|frame|Deleting roads (with CTRL)]]
#Release the mouse and the roads will be sold.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/AutoroadTut8.png|none|frame|A newly deleted roads]]

*The second way is to '''select the Remove tool''' ( [[File:en/Manual/Toggle clear active.png|Clear button]] ). The white squares will change to red squares. Now you can simply '''click & drag''' along the existing roads to remove them. Click the tool button again to deselect it. You can also use the '''R''' key shortcut.

